go.png\" alt=\"Commons OGNL\"/>\n                </a>\n            </div><!-- id=\"bannerRight\" -->\n        <div class=\"clear\">\n        <hr/>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"breadcrumbs\">\n            \n                \n                <div class=\"xleft\">\n        <span id=\"publishDate\">Last Published: 01 March 2013</span>\n                  &nbsp;| <span id=\"projectVersion\">Version: 4.0-SNAPSHOT</span>\n                      </div>\n            <div class=\"xright\">                    <a href=\"http://www.apachecon.com/\" class=\"externalLink\" title=\"ApacheCon\">ApacheCon</a>\n            |\n                        <a href=\"http://www.apache.org\" class=\"externalLink\" title=\"Apache\">Apache</a>\n            |\n                        <a href=\"../\" title=\"Commons\">Commons</a>\n              \n                \n      </div>\n      <div class=\"clear\">\n        <hr/>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"leftColumn\">\n      <div id=\"navcolumn\">\n             \n                \n               \n\n--- https://ognl.orphan.software/\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en-US\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset='utf-8'>\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/assets/css/style.css?v=c5cad493ffc2df8b8130be9bb5ab8ffe65bfb194\">\n    <!-- start custom head snippets, customize with your own _includes/head-custom.html file -->\n\n<!-- Setup theme-color -->\n<!-- start theme color meta headers -->\n<meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#151515\">\n<meta name=\"msapplication-navbutton-color\" content=\"#151515\">\n<meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style\" content=\"black-translucent\">\n<!-- end theme color meta headers -->\n\n\n<!-- Setup Google Analytics -->\n\n\n\n<!-- You can set your favicon here -->\n<!-- link rel=\"shortcut icon\" type=\"image/x-icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" -->\n\n<!-- end custom head snippets -->\n\n\n<!-- Begin Jekyll SEO tag v2.8.0 -->\n<title>OGNL main page | Object-Graph Navigation Language</title>\n<meta name=\"generator\" content=\"Jekyll v3.9.3\" />\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"OGNL main page\" />\n<meta name=\"author\" content=\"Łukasz Lenart\" />\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" />\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"OGNL stands for Object-Graph Navigation Language; it is an expression language for getting and setting properties of Java objects\" />\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"OGNL stands for Object-Graph Navigation Language; it is an expression language for getting and setting properties of Java objects\" />\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://ognl.orphan.software/\" />\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://ognl.orphan.software/\" />\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Object-Graph Navigation Language\" />\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\" />\n<meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary\" />\n<meta property=\"twitter:title\" content=\"OGNL main page\" />\n<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Łukasz Lenart\",\"url\":\"https://lenart.org.pl\"},\"description\":\"OGNL stands for Object-Graph Navigation Language; it is an expression language for getting and setting properties of Java objects\",\"headline\":\"OGNL main page\",\"name\":\"Object-Graph Navigation Language\",\"url\":\"https://ognl.orphan.software/\"}</script>\n<!-- End Jekyll SEO tag -->\n\n  </head>\n\n  <body>\n\n    <header>\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <a id=\"a-title\" href=\"/\">\n          <h1>Object-Graph Navigation Language</h1>\n        </a>\n        <h2>OGNL stands for Object-Graph Navigation Language; it is an expression language for getting and setting properties of Java objects</h2>\n\n        <section id=\"downloads\">\n          \n          <a href=\"https://github.